<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>快速配置 - 健康计算器</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "PingFang SC", "Microsoft YaHei", sans-serif; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%); min-height: 100vh; padding: 20px; }
  .container { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .header { text-align: center; color: #fff; padding: 30px 0 20px; }
  .header h1 { font-size: 24px; }
  .header p { font-size: 14px; opacity: 0.9; margin-top: 6px; }
  .card { background: #fff; border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; margin-bottom: 16px; box-shadow: 0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12); }
  .card h2 { font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 12px; color: #374151; }
  .btn { display: block; width: 100%; padding: 15px; border-radius: 10px; font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; cursor: pointer; border: none; text-align: center; text-decoration: none; margin-bottom: 10px; transition: all 0.2s; }
  .btn-green { background: #10B981; color: #fff; }
  .btn-blue { background: #3B82F6; color: #fff; }
  .btn-purple { background: #8B5CF6; color: #fff; }
  .btn-orange { background: #F59E0B; color: #fff; }
  .btn:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); opacity: 0.95; }
  .input-group { margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .input-group label { font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; color: #374151; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .input-group input { width: 100%; padding: 12px; border: 2px solid #E5E7EB; border-radius: 8px; font-size: 15px; font-family: monospace; }
  .input-group input:focus { outline: none; border-color: #667eea; }
  code { background: #F3F4F6; padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 13px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
  <div class="header">
    <h1>3步上线</h1>
    <p>打开链接创建账号，复制ID，粘贴到下方</p>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>第1步：创建 Google 服务</h2>
    <a class="btn btn-green" href="https://analytics.google.com" target="_blank">打开 GA4 (analytics.google.com)</a>
    <a class="btn btn-blue" href="https://tagmanager.google.com" target="_blank">打开 GTM (tagmanager.google.com)</a>
    <a class="btn btn-purple" href="https://adsense.google.com" target="_blank">打开 AdSense (adsense.google.com)</a>
    <a class="btn btn-orange" href="https://search.google.com/search-console" target="_blank">打开 Search Console</a>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>第2步：粘贴 ID</h2>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>GA4 测量 ID（格式: <code>G-9HDK6XWY7J</code>）</label>
      <input type="text" id="ga4" placeholder="G-" oninput="checkAll()">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>GTM 容器 ID（格式: <code>GTM-N26FR57S</code>）</label>
      <input type="text" id="gtm" placeholder="GTM-" oninput="checkAll()">
    </div>
    <div class="input-group">
      <label>AdSense 发布商 ID（格式: <code>ca-pub-XXXXXXXXXXXX</code>）</label>
      <input type="text" id="adsense" placeholder="ca-pub-" oninput="checkAll()">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="card">
    <h2>第3步：部署</h2>
    <button class="btn btn-green" id="deployBtn" onclick="goDeploy()" disabled>
      跳转到 GitHub 部署
    </button>
    <p style="font-size:12px;color:#6B7280;text-align:center;margin-top:8px;">
      点击后在新页面中点击 "Run workflow" 选择 "仅更新代码" 填入ID
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="card" style="text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-size:13px;color:#6B7280;">
      搞不定？把 ID 直接发给 AI 助手，30秒完成
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<script>
function checkAll() {
  var ga4 = document.getElementById('ga4').value.trim();
  var gtm = document.getElementById('gtm').value.trim();
  var has = (ga4 && ga4 !== 'G-') || (gtm && gtm !== 'GTM-');
  document.getElementById('deployBtn').disabled = !has;
}
function goDeploy() {
  window.open('https://github.com/Cuibingyan-sys/1/actions/workflows/setup-google-services.yml', '_blank');
}
</script>
</body>
</html>